<p><strong>변경일:</strong> 2026. 2. 25. (한국 표준시)</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="리팩토링">리팩토링<a href="https://nhn-commerce-fe.github.io/admin-ui-archive/@ncds/ui-admin/1.5.5/releases/ui-admin/release-note-ui-admin-1.5.4#%EB%A6%AC%ED%8C%A9%ED%86%A0%EB%A7%81" class="hash-link" aria-label="리팩토링에 대한 직접 링크" title="리팩토링에 대한 직접 링크">​</a></h3>
